  <thing id="cEWMFlurry" name="Flurry of Strikes" description="When wielding an exotic double weapon or a spiked chain with both hands, the character can elect to use a full attack action to make a flurry of strikes. When doing so, he may make one extra attack in the round at his full base attack bonus, but this attack takes a &#150;2 penalty, as does each other attack made in that round and until the exotic weapon master&#146;s next turn. The extra attack may be with either end of the double weapon." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Exotic double weapon/spiked chain can flurry, extra att but all take -2 pen." uniqueness="unique">
