  <thing id="cEWMThrow" name="Throw Exotic Weapon" description="The character can throw an exotic weapon with no penalty on the attack roll, even if it isn&#146;t designed to be thrown (such as an orc double axe or a spiked chain). When he throws a double weapon, only one end of the weapon (character&#146;s choice) can strike the target. Exotic weapons thrown in this way have a range increment of 10 feet." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Can throw exotic weapon not normally thrown with 10 ft rng inc &amp; no pen." uniqueness="unique">
