  <thing id="cEWMTrip" name="Trip Attack" description="The character can use a one-handed or two handed exotic weapon to make a trip attack. If he is tripped during his own trip attempt, he can drop the weapon to avoid being tripped. If the exotic weapon already allows its wielder to make trip attacks, the character instead adds a +2 bonus on any trip attempt." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Exotic one or two handed weapon can trip foes, gain +2 bon if already can." uniqueness="unique">
