  <thing id="cEWMExWeS1" name="Exotic Weapon Stunt" description="At each level, an exotic weapon master learns a special trick that he can use with any exotic weapon for which he has the Weapon Focus feat. He must select the trick learned when he gains the level, and once selected, the choice cannot later be changed. He can&#146;t select the same stunt more than once." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You can select an Exotic Weapon Stunt.">
