  <thing id="fimpRapSho" name="Improved Rapid Shot" description="You are an expert at firing weapons with exceptional speed.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Manyshot, Point Blank Shot, Rapid Shot.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: When using the Rapid Shot feat, you may ignore the &#150;2 penalty on all your ranged attack rolls.\n\n{b}Special{/b}: A fighter may select Improved Rapid Shot as one of his fighter bonus feats.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Warrior" compset="Feat" summary="Rapid shot no longer imposes -2 penalty." uniqueness="useronce">
