      ~ Otherwise, add a +2 Shield bonus to our AC
      hero.child[ArmorClass].field[tACShield].value = maximum(hero.child[ArmorClass].field[tACShield].value, 2)]]></eval>
    <eval phase="UserPreLv" index="2"><![CDATA[~ Done by Lawful_G
