  <thing id="fExtraSmCW" name="Extra Smiting" description="You can make more smite attacks.\n\n{b}Prerequisites{/b}: Smite ability, base attack bonus +4.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: When you take this feat, you gain two extra attempts to smite per day. Use whatever smite ability you have (the paladin&#146;s smite evil ability or the hunter of the dead&#146;s ability to smite undead, for example).\n\n{b}Special{/b}: You can take this feat multiple times. Its effects stack.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Warrior" compset="Feat" summary="Two extra smites per day.">
