  <thing id="cJusBrinBA" name="Bring &apos;em Back Alive" description="Whenever a justiciar attacks with a melee weapon, he can deal nonlethal damage with the weapon instead of lethal damage with no penalty on the attack roll. Normally, attempting to deal nonlethal damage with a weapon in this way incurs a &#150;4 penalty on the attack roll." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You may use melee weapons to deal non-lethal damage at no penalty." sortorder="1">
