  <thing id="cJusCripSt" name="Crippling Strike" description="A justiciar of 2nd level or higher can make a nonlethal strike against an opponent with such precision that his blow weakens and hampers the opponent. When a justiciar damages an opponent with a nonlethal strike, that character also takes 1 point of Strength damage." compset="ClSpecial" summary="When using Nonlethal Strike, target also takes 1 point Str damage." sortorder="2">
