  <thing id="cKensai" name="Kensai" description="The kensai masters body, mind, weapon and will. He devotes his strength and his life to the service of a master or an ideal he accepts as greater than himself. \n\nHe must swear an Oath of Service (see details on Complete Warrior) to enter this prestige class.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Warrior" compset="ClassLevel" maxlimit="10">
