  <thing id="cOSlVicStr" name="Vicious Strike" description="At 2nd level and higher, an occult slayer who readies an attack action to disrupt a spellcaster deals double damage if the attack hits." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Readied attack to disrupt spellcasters deals double damage.">
