  <thing id="cvRgrNoSpl" name="Ranger (No Spells)" description="The variant ranger gains all the normal class features of the ranger, with the following changes and additions.\n\n{b}Spells{/b}: The ranger does not gain the ability to cast divine spells.\n\n{b}Fast Movement (Ex){/b}: At 6th level, the ranger&#146;s base land speed increases by 10 feet. This benefit applies only when he is wearing no armor, light armor, or medium armor and not carrying a heavy load.\n\n{b}Nature&#146;s Blessing (Su){/b}: At 11th level and higher, the ranger can use a standard action to add a +4 bonus to his Constitution, Dexterity, or Wisdom score. This ability may be used once per day, and its effect lasts for 1 minute per class level.\n\n{b}{i}Healing Touch{/i} (Sp){/b}: Once per day, a ranger of 13th level or higher can use either {i}neutralize poison{/i} or {i}remove disease{/i}, as a caster whose level is equal to one-half the ranger&#146;s class level.\n\n{b}{i}Freedom of Movement{/i} (Sp){/b}: A ranger of 16th level or higher can use {i}freedom of movement{/i} on himself once per day, as a caster whose level is equal to one-half the ranger&#146;s class level.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Warrior" compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
