  <thing id="cvRgrFastM" name="Fast Movement" description="At 6th level, the ranger&#146;s base land speed increases by 10 feet. This benefit applies only when he is wearing no armor, light armor, or medium armor and not carrying a heavy load." compset="ClSpecial" summary="+10 feet to speed, unless heavily loaded.">
