  <thing id="cRMaSleepL" name="Sleeper Lock" description="At 3rd level, a reaping mauler learns how to render an opponent unconscious with pressure. If the character pins his opponent while grappling and maintains the pin for 1 full round, the opponent must make a Fortitude save (DC 10 + the reaping mauler&#146;s class level + the reaping mauler&#146;s Wis modifier) at the end of the round or fall unconscious for 1d3 rounds. A creature with no discernible anatomy has immunity to this effect." compset="ClSpecial" summary="If maintain pin 1 full round, foe is unconscious for 1d3 rds (DCXX Fort neg)." sortorder="3">
