  <thing id="cRMaDevGra" name="Devastating Grapple" description="If a 5th-level reaping mauler pins his opponent while grappling and maintains the pin for 3 consecutive rounds, the opponent must make a Fortitude save (DC 10 + the reaping mauler&#146;s class level + the reaping mauler&#146;s Wis modifier) at the end of the third round or die. A creature with no discernible anatomy is immune to the effect of this ability." compset="ClSpecial" summary="If maintain pin 3 full rounds, foe dies (DCXX Fort neg)." sortorder="5">
