  <thing id="cSMIStare" name="Staredown" description="At 6th level, a samurai becomes able to strike fear into his foes by his mere presence. He gains a +4 bonus on Intimidate checks and can demoralize an opponent (as described in the Intimidate skill description, page 76 of the Player&#146;s Handbook)." compset="ClSpecial">
