  <thing id="cSMIFriPre" name="Frightful Presence" description="A 20th-level samurai&#146;s bravery, honor, and fighting prowess have become legendary. When the samurai draws his blade, opponents within 30 feet must\nsucceed on a Will save (DC 20 + samurai&#146;s Cha modifier) or become panicked for 4d6 rounds (if they have 4 or fewer Hit Dice) or shaken for 4d6 rounds (if they have from 5 to 19 Hit Dice). Creatures with 20 or more Hit Dice are not affected. Any foe that successfully resists the effect cannot be affected again by the same samurai&#146;s frightful presence for 24 hours." compset="ClSpecial">
