  <thing id="cSpSBonFea" name="Bonus Feat" description="At 2nd level, a spellsword advances his art, gaining a bonus feat. This bonus feat must be either a metamagic feat or one drawn from the list of bonus feats allowed to a fighter (see Table 5&#150;1 on page 90 of the Player&#146;s Handbook)." compset="ClSpecial" summary="You gain either a metamagic or fighter bonus feat.">
