  <thing id="cSwbLucky" name="Lucky" description="Many swashbucklers live by the credo &#147;Better lucky than good.&#148; Once per day, a swashbuckler of 11th level or higher may reroll any failed attack roll, skill check, ability check, or saving throw. The character must take the result of the reroll, even if it&#146;s worse than the original roll." compset="ClSpecial" summary="1/day, reroll failed attack, save, skill or ability check, must take new result.">
