  <thing id="cSwbSlMind" name="Slippery Mind" description="When a swashbuckler reaches 17th level, her mind becomes more difficult to control. If the swashbuckler fails her save against an enchantment spell or effect, she can attempt the save again 1 round later at the same DC (assuming she is still alive). She gets only this one extra chance to succeed at a certain saving throw." compset="ClSpecial" summary="When fail save vs enchantment, may retry save on next rd once.">
