      hero.child[aCON].field[aNormMod].value += 4]]></eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cWaSMorRea" name="Morphic Reach" description="A warshaper of 3rd level or higher can suddenly stretch its limbs, neck, or other appendages outward, giving it 5 more feet of reach than the creature it&#146;s emulating. Unlike most creatures, warshapers don&#146;t appear to have a longer reach until they actually use it." compset="ClSpecial" summary="May stretch any part of body, giving +5 ft to reach.">
