  <thing id="cWaSMorHea" name="Morphic Healing" description="At 4th level, a warshaper becomes able to change its form where wounds appear, creating smooth skin where once were wounds. The warshaper gains fast healing 2, and if it spends a full-round action and succeeds on a Concentration check (DC equal to the total damage it has sustained), it heals 10 points of damage." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Full rd, heal 10 dam by making conc ck (DC = current dam).">
