  <thing id="wDartBlowG" name="Dart, Blowgun" description="A blowgun dart resembles a lightweight, undersized arrow. You don&#146;t apply your Strength modifier to damage with a blowgun dart. A blowgun dart can&#146;t effectively be used as a melee weapon. Blowgun darts come in a leather pouch that holds 10 darts. A dart that hits its target is destroyed; one that misses has a 50% chance to be destroyed or lost.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Complete Warrior" compset="Weapon" lotsize="10" stacking="merge">
