  <thing id="cKoCHolAur" name="{i}{b}Holy Aura{/b}{/i} 1/day" description="A 10th-level knight of the Chalice has the ability to create a {i}holy aura{/i} once per day that affects herself only. The aura&#146;s effect is as the spell cast by a 10th-level cleric, but it wards the knight against the attacks, spells, and mental infl uence of evil outsiders only, and only evil outsiders can be blinded if they strike the knight." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Create {i}holy aura{/i} effect on yourself once per day.">
