  <thing id="cTMkArrow" name="Arrowroot" description="A character with this tattoo can heal wounds in another character by touch. Each day he can cure a total number of hit points equal to his Wisdom bonus &#215; his class level. A tattooed monk cannot heal himself, but he may divide the curing among multiple recipients, and he doesn&#146;t have to use it all at once." compset="CustomSpec" summary="Heal others with a touch." uniqueness="useronce">
